{"tid":2207172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫錯開10倍藥量 男一吃慘喪失性功能","createTime":"2020-09-18T04:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T12:26:14.000Z","uid":135488,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b07c6169a34f45e36fbf908ff815ec2c5f055a6a","tid":2207172,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:05:20.000Z","msg":"中國一名男子因為皮膚病到醫院看診，但醫生開的藥量是正常人的10倍，讓男子吃了3天後感覺不適進加護病房搶救，男子的妻子稱，丈夫現在嚴重後遺症、生活不能自理，喪失性能力。<br />\n<br />\n據《澎湃新聞》報導，9月10日，朱女指出，她的丈夫孫男於今年4月13日因皮膚瘙癢，到廣西醫科大學第二附屬醫院就診，服用過量藥物後昏迷，送到加護病房進行治療。朱女質疑，丈夫昏迷、休克與醫生錯開過量藥物有關，因為一次最多服用2、3片的「雷公藤多苷片」，醫生竟要求孫男一次服用20片。<br />\n<br />\n朱女稱，醫院工作人員曾和她多次溝通，並承認系醫療事故。但雙方未就孫先生的治療問題達成一致意見。朱女說，丈夫現在有嚴重後遺症、生活不能自理，喪失性能力，但醫院卻一直讓他們出院。 夫婦兩人不同意醫院的判斷，至今仍拒絕出院。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200916/EAMLAZ77R5BKJCDVFC2O3TKKRA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200916%2FEAMLAZ77R5BKJCDVFC2O3TKKRA%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=89ea235c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200916%2FEAMLAZ77R5BKJCDVFC2O3TKKRA%2F&h=8bf68f40\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200916/EAMLAZ77R5BKJCDVFC2O3TKKRA/</a>"},{"pid":"8f18c1b425e5a1cdfdcfa674eb61091e0d93597e","tid":2207172,"uid":146520,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"繼續派啲支那專才嚟囉，遲早香港就每年幾十單咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7511f94db87d669324fea4977d9477af7b991842","tid":2207172,"uid":135488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"